item.title: The TIlehurst End Podcast Episode 390: Sad Face Emoji
item.description:
The boys weigh in on a truly miserable week in Berkshire, with another takeover failing to be completed, and the team falling to a 5-2 loss in Bolton. There’s discussion of the definition of “garbage time”, the admirable lack of quit in the players, and the exciting upcoming match for the U21s. Thanks as always to our friends at ZCZ Films for sponsoring the pod
